00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:22,375
Keep that in mind, and no
matter what challenges arise,

265
00:14:22,458 --> 00:14:24,125
don't get yourself killed.

266
00:14:27,041 --> 00:14:30,125
[PIETRO crying]

267
00:14:33,791 --> 00:14:35,916
