296
00:15:58,708 --> 00:16:00,375
You ready for this, Frenchy?

297
00:16:01,791 --> 00:16:03,791
After all the hard work
required to funnel

298
00:16:03,875 --> 00:16:05,625
France's power into Durandal,

299
00:16:05,708 --> 00:16:08,291
I couldn't be more
ready to finally use it.

300
00:16:15,750 --> 00:16:18,791
[CARISSA] Let's see what
