00:16:32,916 --> 00:16:35,916
and help us battle
Academy City's top forces.

308
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:38,500
First, we'll destroy the
unmanned units' command center.

309
00:16:38,583 --> 00:16:40,500
[FIAMMA laughing]

310
00:16:40,583 --> 00:16:42,500
Let me make sure I understand.

311
00:16:42,583 --> 00:16:45,000
You have the archangel
of water at your disposal

312
00:16:45,083 --> 00:16:46,583
and you want me
to damage a building

313
00:16:46,666 --> 00:16:47,750
as the first attack?

314
00:16:47,833 --> 00:16:49,333
[NIKOLAI]
What are you trying to say?

315
00:16:49,416 --> 00:16:51,916
[FIAMMA] Just that it makes
sense now why you got no further

316
00:16:52,000 --> 00:16:53,458
