329
00:17:22,041 --> 00:17:23,750
With just one word
from me, your fortress

330
00:17:23,833 --> 00:17:25,458
would disintegrate.

331
00:17:25,541 --> 00:17:28,625
And how would you handle
that, Fiamma?

332
00:17:28,708 --> 00:17:30,708
[FIAMMA laughs]

333
00:17:30,791 --> 00:17:33,208
If that's the best retort
you could do after giving it

334
00:17:33,291 --> 00:17:37,416
serious thought, then it's
a wonder you even made bishop.

335
00:17:37,500 --> 00:17:39,583
There's a good reason I went
to the trouble of acquiring

336
00:17:39,666 --> 00:17:43,500
the remote-control magical item
for the 103,000 grimoires.

337
00:17:43,583 --> 00:17:46,791
Hold on! You can use them?

338
00:17:46,875 --> 00:17:48,791
You're able to use powers
other than those

339
00:17:48,875 --> 00:17:50,541
of the Right Seat of God?

340
00:17:50,625 --> 00:17:52,833
[FIAMMA] For me to become
the Person Superior to God,

341
00:17:52,916 --> 00:17:54,750
I must have separate powers.

342
00:17:54,833 --> 00:17:57,583
And so, while it pains me to
end our fruitful partnership,

343
00:17:57,666 --> 00:17:59,500
your usefulness to me
is at an end.

344
00:17:59,583 --> 00:18:03,666
Thus, I will now be disposing
of your 200 sorcerers.

345
00:18:03,750 --> 00:18:06,000
Don't spend too much
time dwelling on this.

346
00:18:06,083 --> 00:18:08,666
Seek to find the glory
in your defeat.

347
00:18:11,833 --> 00:18:12,833
Damn it!

348
00:18:24,583 --> 00:18:26,458
[yelling]

349
00:18:27,750 --> 00:18:29,375
[yelling]

350
00:18:33,750 --> 00:18:35,291
[MISHA]
Air precedence sword.

351
00:18:39,833 --> 00:18:42,083
[MISHA] Wind precedence
ground and human.

352
00:18:47,541 --> 00:18:48,583
[FEMME FATALE gasps]

353
00:18:51,250 --> 00:18:53,083
Do you have any
idea what that was?

354
00:18:53,166 --> 00:18:54,500
I couldn't even make it out.

355
00:18:54,583 --> 00:18:57,291
Gabriel is known
as a message bearer.

356
00:18:57,375 --> 00:18:59,916
She's diverting our
instincts and foresight.

357
00:19:00,000 --> 00:19:02,833
Rely only on your
five primary senses.

358
00:19:02,916 --> 00:19:05,583
Using your sixth sense will
throw your timing off.

359
00:19:05,666 --> 00:19:07,208
[MISHA] You are not effective.
Not effective.

360
00:19:07,291 --> 00:19:08,458
You are nothing.

361
00:19:08,541 --> 00:19:10,291
The more we fight her,
the more she seems to be

362
00:19:10,375 --> 00:19:11,875
