363
00:19:11,958 --> 00:19:14,875
You're the one who encouraged
her with that sword of yours.

364
00:19:23,000 --> 00:19:24,125
[CARISSA grunts]

365
00:19:27,083 --> 00:19:28,916
What's taking so long,
you barbarian?

366
00:19:29,000 --> 00:19:30,750
Isn't your Curtana
supposed to be chock full

367
00:19:30,833 --> 00:19:32,500
