378
00:20:18,750 --> 00:20:19,750
[FEMME FATALE gasps]

379
00:20:20,750 --> 00:20:22,291
[CARISSA]
I know how this looks.

380
00:20:22,375 --> 00:20:25,250
It does stand to reason that if
my Curtana Second fragment

381
00:20:25,333 --> 00:20:29,125
