386
00:20:47,041 --> 00:20:48,958
[MISHA]
The damage has been confirmed.

387
00:20:49,041 --> 00:20:50,000
Over.

388
00:20:51,583 --> 00:20:53,000
[CARISSA] How long do
you think it will take before

389
00:20:53,083 --> 00:20:56,166
