401
00:21:19,291 --> 00:21:21,541
I'd prefer if you didn't place
things we need in there.

402
00:21:21,625 --> 00:21:24,166
Speaking as a fellow woman,
I find it disturbing.

403
00:21:25,666 --> 00:21:28,125
Attention all
military on standby!

