00:22:18,833 --> 00:22:19,791
Um...

417
00:22:22,125 --> 00:22:23,208
What the--?

418
00:22:29,916 --> 00:22:31,166
[KAMIJO]
Misha Kruezhev!

419
00:22:36,000 --> 00:22:37,041
